DNA_sequence is Chase’s full genome string (stored only in the master node, never transmitted).

node_salt is a random 32‑byte value stored in the node’s secure element during initial pairing.

The HKDF (HMAC‑based Key Derivation Function) produces a 256‑bit key suitable for AES‑256.

