Layer Purpose Key Source Scope
Node storage Encrypt raw sensor data DNA‑derived + node unique key Isolated per node
RF traffic Encrypt node‑to‑node communication Session key (ephemeral) Between any two nodes
Blockchain anchor Prove data existence None (only hash) Public / cross‑network
Backup to cloud Encrypt before uploading User‑provided password + DNA Entire dataset
